Definition: any of various shrubs of the genus Deutzia having usually toothed opposite leaves and shredding bark and white or pink flowers in loose terminal clusters
Synonyms: hydrangea, genus_Deutzia, m, any, of, various, shrubs, the, genus, Deutzia, having, usually, toothed, opposite, leaves, and, shredding, bark, white, or, pink, flowers, in, loose, terminal, clusters
Category: noun.plant
